</P>
<P>
 Term expires: 1998 
</P>
<P>
 Key issues: City's budget is a major concern. He noted Villa Park already has 
decided to delay a $200,000 improvement of Cerro Villa Drive because of the 
county bankruptcy. He said he is also concerned about how the expansion of Loma 
Street will affect traffic in Villa Park. 
