 Jari Kurri of the Kings led all scorers with nine points in hockey's European 
Cup as a member of Finnish champion Jokerit of Helsinki. College Football 
</P>
<P>
 Charlie Weatherbie, who led Utah State to its first bowl victory -- over Ball 
State in the 1993 Las Vegas Bowl -- is the new coach at Navy. 
</P>
<P>
 Weatherbie, 39, replaces George Chaump, fired after going 14-41-0 in five 
seasons. 
</P>
<P>
