<P>
HOST OF PARADES, SPECIALS AND YEAR-END ROUNDUPS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By N.F. MENDOZA 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 There may be surprises in your resolutions this New Year, but don't look for 
something completely different in television programming. In the offering: the 
annual -- and traditional -- roundup of parades and New Year celebrations. 
</P>
<P>
 The public affairs shows are highlighted by year-end reviews and looks ahead 
to 1995. 
</P>
<P>
 Other weekend shows include: N.F. MENDOZA 
</P>
</TEXT>
