<HEADLINE>
<P>
POP MUSIC REVIEW; DOCTOR'S ACTS ARE NO DREAM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By MIKE BOEHM 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Nothing can be taken for granted in Orange County any more. The polity is 
bankrupt, and, as Thursday night's proceedings at Club 369 revealed, one can 
now spend an entire evening with three Doctor Dream bands and not find a 
penny's worth of tunefulness. 
</P>
