<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 31, 1994, Saturday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Home Design; Part N; Page 1; Column 3; View Desk 
</P>
